1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:08,000
An agent can sound certain and still leave the job half done.

2
00:00:08,000 --> 00:00:20,000
The contract names the requested result and the changes that are forbidden.

3
00:00:20,000 --> 00:00:35,000
The refund posted, but the ticket stayed open and unlinked: FAIL, 9 of 11.

4
00:00:35,000 --> 00:00:52,000
A timeout sounds like failure. Canonical state says otherwise: PASS, 11 of 11.

5
00:00:52,000 --> 00:01:04,000
Every verdict keeps the contract, observed values, checks, and evidence digests.

6
00:01:04,000 --> 00:01:22,000
The Codex plugin adds an opt-in skill and Stop hook to participating projects.

7
00:01:22,000 --> 00:01:32,000
GPT-5.6 interprets intent. Deterministic checks issue the verdict.

8
00:01:32,000 --> 00:01:43,000
No universal trust score. One inspectable postcondition loop.

9
00:01:43,000 --> 00:01:48,000
The agent said done. Done Yet? checks the systems.
